title: Wildlands Field Studies in Chile
text:
I participated in a 6 week field study course in Northern Patagonia in winter 2024. I received academic course credit towards my major, but also invaluable hands on experience, friendships, personal growth, and field skills.



Quick selfie with the sunset over Volcan Osorno from our camp on the northern flank of Volcan Calbuco
